    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.9-beta.1</title>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 19:56:48 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>202602232056</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.9-beta.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:channel>beta</sparkle:channel>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Continuous avatar detection via MutationObserver — watches DOM for the user's profile picture appearing after QR scan or session restore</li>
<li>Periodic avatar refresh every 5 minutes to detect WhatsApp profile picture changes</li>
</ul>
<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Rewrote avatar probing with 6 modern strategies targeting WhatsApp Web 2025+ layout (data-testid selectors, webpack cache scan, profile panel click)</li>
<li>Split avatar probing into quick (DOM scan) and deep (click) modes to minimize UI disruption</li>
<li>Extended avatar probe window from 90s (12 attempts) to ~3.5min (18 attempts) with adaptive timing</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fixed avatar not showing for account profile — probing now uses modern WhatsApp Web selectors instead of deprecated nav/Store APIs</li>
<li>Fixed blob URL avatar extraction using fetch+FileReader instead of canvas (avoids CORS taint errors)</li>
</ul>]]></description>
